ambiguous terms,

17:23.000 --> 17:25.000
such as, it's the presence,

17:25.000 --> 17:27.000
presence of things.

17:27.000 --> 17:29.000
The fact that things are

17:29.000 --> 17:31.000
present means consciousness is there.

17:31.000 --> 17:33.000
Obviously, people can now

17:33.000 --> 17:35.000
overdo that,

17:35.000 --> 17:37.000
and then end up

17:37.000 --> 17:39.000
mystifying consciousness,

