24:17.000 --> 24:19.000
Hmm.

24:19.000 --> 24:21.000
Displeasing.

24:21.000 --> 24:23.000
How it happens in the mind of our hunter?

24:23.000 --> 24:25.000
Displeasing.

24:25.000 --> 24:27.000
Displeasingness.

24:27.000 --> 24:29.000
Oh, this is disagreeable.

24:29.000 --> 24:31.000
It's a feeling.

