24:39.000 --> 24:41.000
ill will or aversion?

24:41.000 --> 24:43.000
Hmm.

24:43.000 --> 24:45.000
If you can see that, then, oh, keep doing it.

24:45.000 --> 24:47.000
And then you learn how to be displeased

24:47.000 --> 24:49.000
without being angry.

24:49.000 --> 24:51.000
Hmm. Which means you free yourself from anger.

24:51.000 --> 24:53.000
Hmm.

24:53.000 --> 24:55.000
But

24:55.000 --> 24:57.000
you can't, like, feeling

24:57.000 --> 24:59.000
as feeling for a protugina

