So it's not.

27:39.000 --> 27:41.000
Sotabati, seven,

27:41.000 --> 27:43.000
or something like that.

27:43.000 --> 27:45.000
It's a guideline.

27:45.000 --> 27:47.000
It's like a little

27:47.000 --> 27:51.000
stopping points

27:51.000 --> 27:53.000
of one, actually,

